<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="year-n">year <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /jɪə(r), jɜ:(r)/    美 /jɪr/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(日历) 年</strong></h4>
<h4 id="2">2.<strong>年度；学年：年级：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am in my first year at senior high school.
我是高中一年级学生。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>...岁</strong></h4>
<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[非正式用语] 很长时间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I haven’t played the piano for years. 
我很久没弹钢琴了。</p><footer>2012 湖南</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-the-year-round">all (the) year round</h3>
<p>1.<strong>一年到头：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Antarctic is covered with snow and ice all year round. 
南极地区终年被冰雪覆盖。</p><footer>北师大③ – 7</footer></div>

<h3 id="year-after-year">year after year</h3>
<p>1.<strong>年复一年：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Year after year he had to work hard to get out of debt. 
年复一年，为了还债他不得不拼命工作。</p></div>

<h3 id="year-by-year">year by year</h3>
<p>1.<strong>年年；逐年：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Year by year my father became weaker. 
我父亲的身体一年比一年差。</p></div></div>